Package Extbase\DomainObject

Interface summary

Tx_Extbase_DomainObject_DomainObjectInterface A Domain Object Interface. All domain objects which should be persisted need to implement the below interface.

Class summary

Tx_Extbase_DomainObject_AbstractDomainObject A generic Domain Object.
Tx_Extbase_DomainObject_AbstractEntity An abstract Entity. An Entity is an object fundamentally defined not by its attributes, but by a thread of continuity and identity (e.g. a person).
Tx_Extbase_DomainObject_AbstractValueObject A abstract Value Object. A Value Object is an object that describes some characteristic or attribute (e.g. a color) but carries no concept of identity.
